1
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:35,622
Thanks for watching!

2
00:00:56,207 --> 00:01:07,230
Thanks for watching!

3
00:01:21,772 --> 00:01:33,623
Thanks for watching!

4
00:02:07,775 --> 00:02:36,887
Namo Tassa Bhagavato Arahato Sambha Sambhudassa Namo Tassa Bhagavato Arahato Sambha Sambhudassa Namo Tassa Bhagavato Arahato Sambha Sambhudassa

5
00:02:37,627 --> 00:03:06,569
Pahamnawerohomi, Abhyavajohomi, Anigohomi, Sukhiathananpariharami, Dukhamujami, Yathaladasampatitho, Mawikachami, Amakanchatupachayadayaka,

6
00:03:06,819 --> 00:03:28,794
Avera hontu, abhya bhaja hontu, Aniga hontu, sukhya tanam pariharantu, Dukhamu chantu, yathalada sampatito, Mawika chantu.

7
00:03:29,314 --> 00:03:52,064
Amaka marta apitu acharyan yati mita samuha Avera hantu abhya bhaja hantu Aniga hantu sukhya tanam hari haramtu

8
00:03:52,467 --> 00:04:11,995
Dukhamu Chantu Yathaladha Sampatito Mawika Chantu Imasmin Vihare Sabeh Bhikkhu Saba Bhikkhu Ni Sabeh Acharya

9
00:04:12,262 --> 00:04:37,341
Sabe yogino Avera hontu Abhya bhaja hontu Anika hontu Sukhi atanam Pari haramtu Dukhamu chantu Yathalada sampatito Mavika chantu

10
00:04:37,675 --> 00:05:03,057
Arakadevata Averahontu Abhyavajahontu Anigahontu Sukhyatanam Hariharantu Dudukahuchantu Yathaladasampatito Mavikachantu

11
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:27,932
Imaslingame janapade Yoropaya lokasmin sabejanata Awerahontu abhyabhajahontu Anighahontu sukhiatanam pariharantu

12
00:05:27,911 --> 00:05:57,632
Dukhamu Cantu Yathalada Sampatitho Mawika Cantu Puratimaya Disaya Pacimaya Disaya Putaraya Disaya Dakhinaya Disaya Puratimaya Ludhisaya Pacimaya Ludhisaya

13
00:05:58,168 --> 00:06:11,588
Uttaraya Anudisaya Dakinaya Anudisaya Hetimaya Disaya Uparimaya Disaya

14
00:06:12,242 --> 00:06:40,495
Sabe sata, sabe pana, sabe buta, sabe bukhala, sabe atavavapariya pana, sabe itiyo, sabe purisa, sabe ariya, sabe anariya, sabe deva, sabe manusa,

15
00:06:40,778 --> 00:06:43,781
Sabe winipatika.

16
00:06:44,783 --> 00:06:56,778
Awera hontu, Abhyabhaja hontu, Aniga hontu, Sukhi hatanam, Pariharantu.

17
00:06:57,519 --> 00:07:06,550
Dukhamu chantu, Yathalata sampatito, Mawika chantu.

18
00:07:07,339 --> 00:07:15,233
Metta Bhavana.

19
00:07:16,293 --> 00:07:19,560
Developing goodwill, loving-kindness.

20
00:07:20,922 --> 00:07:23,084
May you be safe, well and happy.

21
00:07:23,887 --> 00:07:27,833
May you live contented, in harmony with the world.

22
00:07:29,875 --> 00:07:32,841
So we can bring to mind some of our benefactors.

23
00:07:55,702 --> 00:07:57,946
Those who are near and dear to us.

24
00:07:57,985 --> 00:08:23,701
Friends, people at work, whomever we wish.

25
00:08:50,884 --> 00:09:16,673
a neutral person towards ourselves

26
00:09:39,417 --> 00:10:06,032
someone we have difficulties with towards each other

27
00:10:28,961 --> 00:10:56,370
all those in our neighborhood, all the people in our country,

28
00:11:19,620 --> 00:11:21,863
All the peoples of Europe.

29
00:11:45,485 --> 00:11:47,248
All people on earth.

30
00:12:10,499 --> 00:12:38,869
and to all beings in all directions Mudita, developing joy

31
00:12:40,654 --> 00:12:50,629
The traditional blessings, may you be joyful, may you be ever more joyful, may you experience the bliss of Nibbana.

32
00:12:53,735 --> 00:12:58,883
Let's bring to mind moments of joyfulness, happiness we've experienced today.

33
00:13:12,024 --> 00:13:14,727
Let us wish ourselves to be joyful.

34
00:13:47,446 --> 00:13:51,063
Let's bring to mind somebody we know who has cause to be joyful.

35
00:13:51,827 --> 00:13:53,355
Wish them greater joy.

36
00:14:26,123 --> 00:14:53,227
Let us bring to mind that at this moment there are people who are happy and content with their lives, who are enjoying the warmth of various types of friendship from intimate to acquaintance, who enjoy the delights of art, nature, sport, hobbies and so on, who find their work meaningful, who are reaping the fruitfulness of their spiritual practice,

37
00:14:54,169 --> 00:14:57,462
and who rejoice in the success of others.

38
00:15:30,197 --> 00:15:58,904
Let's offer our goodwill joy to all beings in all directions.

39
00:15:59,408 --> 00:16:05,756
Pujachapujanianam etamanggalambuttamam.

40
00:16:06,758 --> 00:16:13,386
Patirupadesavasuchapubechakatapunyata.

41
00:16:14,227 --> 00:16:20,076
Atasamapanidicha etamanggalambuttamam.

42
00:16:21,097 --> 00:16:27,626
Bahusachamchasipanchawinayochasusikitho.

43
00:16:28,147 --> 00:16:34,254
Subhasita jaya wacha etamanggalam uttamam.

44
00:16:35,296 --> 00:16:41,524
Mata pitu upatana buddha terasa sanggaho.

45
00:16:42,466 --> 00:16:48,013
Anakulaca kamanta etamanggalam uttamam.

46
00:16:49,115 --> 00:16:56,043
Daunam ca dhamma charya chanya takanam ca sanggaho.

47
00:16:56,345 --> 00:17:02,253
A-na-wa-ja-ni-ka-ma-ni-e-ta-ma-ngal-ang-bu-ta-ma.

48
00:17:03,835 --> 00:17:09,701
A-ra-ti-we-ra-ti-pa-pa-ma-cha-pa-na-cha-sa-nya-mo.

49
00:17:10,963 --> 00:17:16,691
A-pa-ma-do-cha-da-me-su-e-ta-ma-ngal-ang-bu-ta-ma.

50
00:17:17,852 --> 00:17:24,681
Ga-ra-wa-ja-ni-wa-to-cha-sa-tu-ti-cha-ka-ta-nyu-ta.

51
00:17:25,083 --> 00:17:31,170
Kalena dhamma savanam etamangalam gutamam.

52
00:17:32,271 --> 00:17:38,358
Kantica suvaca sata samananam ca dasanam.

53
00:17:39,059 --> 00:17:45,086
Kalena dhamma sakapca etamangalam gutamam.

54
00:17:46,088 --> 00:17:52,997
Tapuca brahmacaryaca aryasacca nadasanam.

55
00:17:53,382 --> 00:17:59,589
Nibbāna sācci kīryācchā etta maṅgalam uttamam.

56
00:18:00,611 --> 00:18:07,038
Bhūtā salokadāme hi citta yasana kāmpati.

57
00:18:08,039 --> 00:18:14,107
Āsokam vīrajāṅ keman etta maṅgalam uttamam.

58
00:18:15,234 --> 00:18:30,492
EDHA DISANI KADVANA SABHATTA MAPARAJITSA SABHATTA SULTINGA CHANTI KAMTESA MANGALAM UTTAMANTI

59
00:18:31,721 --> 00:18:37,489
Sabe sata sukita hantu.

60
00:18:37,509 --> 00:19:00,717
Sadhu, sadhu, sadhu.

